        <item>
            <title>Apple Intelligence 4 月登陆 Apple Vision Pro——visionOS 2.4 推出多项强大功能</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/22/apple-vision-pro-7/vr-mr-ar/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=apple-vision-pro-7</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/22/apple-vision-pro-7/vr-mr-ar/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 22 Feb 2025 06:01:22 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[VR 科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple Vision Pro]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1293516</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p data-start="74" data-end="346">Apple 宣布 Apple Intelligence 将于 4 月正式登陆 Apple Vision Pro，为空间计算带来更高层次的人工智能应用。新功能包括「书写工具」支援文字修改与 ChatGPT 整合、「影像乐园」提供 AI 生成影像创作，以及 Genmoji 让用户创作个人化表情符号。此外 visionOS 2.4 亦推出全新「Spatial Gallery」app，带来艺术与娱乐内容体验；iPhone 版「Apple Vision Pro」app 亦同步登场，让用户可透过 iPhone 管理 Vision Pro 应用与设定。</p><p data-start="74" data-end="346"><p data-start="74" data-end="346"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293523" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/vlcsnap2025022213h57-4-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/vlcsnap2025022213h57-4-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/vlcsnap2025022213h57-4.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p data-start="74" data-end="346"><h2 data-start="348" data-end="394"><strong data-start="353" data-end="394">Apple Intelligence 强化 Vision Pro 使用体验</strong></h2><p data-start="396" data-end="585">Apple Intelligence 为 Vision Pro 带来多项 AI 功能，提升生产力与创造力。「书写工具」让用户能够在「邮件」、「备忘录」及其他应用中重写、校对与撮写文字，甚至利用 ChatGPT 从零开始生成内容。透过「重写」功能，用户可调整语气，使文字更专业、友好或简洁，而「校对」则可检查文法并提供修改建议。「撮写」功能可将选取文字转换为不同格式的摘要。</p><p data-start="396" data-end="585"><p data-start="396" data-end="585"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293518" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/applevisionos24apple-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/applevisionos24apple-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/applevisionos24apple-1-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p data-start="396" data-end="585"><p data-start="587" data-end="699">「影像乐园」则让 Vision Pro 用户以 AI 创建独特影像，根据输入的描述生成相应画面，甚至可透过个人相片库创作与家人或朋友相似的影像。这项功能整合至「讯息」与「Freeform」等应用，也可作为独立 app 使用。</p><p data-start="587" data-end="699"><p data-start="587" data-end="699"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293525" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/vlcsnap2025022213h56-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/vlcsnap2025022213h56-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/vlcsnap2025022213h56-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p data-start="587" data-end="699"><p data-start="701" data-end="797">Genmoji 让用户能透过 AI 创造个人化表情符号，这些 Genmoji 可嵌入讯息、转换为贴图，或用于「点按回应」。而「智慧型回复」功能则能根据讯息内容提供建议回复，提升沟通效率。</p><p data-start="701" data-end="797"><p data-start="701" data-end="797"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293524" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/vlcsnap2025022213h56-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/vlcsnap2025022213h56-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/vlcsnap2025022213h56.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p data-start="701" data-end="797"><h2 data-start="799" data-end="825"><strong data-start="804" data-end="825">「制作回忆影片」与 AI 搜寻相片</strong></h2><p data-start="827" data-end="958">Apple Intelligence 亦强化「相片」app，透过「制作回忆影片」功能，用户只需输入简单描述，AI 便会从相片库中挑选最适合的影像与影片，组成具故事性的影片，并搭配音乐。「自然语言搜寻」功能允许用户以简单描述搜寻特定相片或影片，无需手动筛选。</p><p data-start="827" data-end="958"><p data-start="827" data-end="958"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293520" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/vlcsnap2025022213h57-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/vlcsnap2025022213h57-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/vlcsnap2025022213h57-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p data-start="827" data-end="958"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293519" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/vlcsnap2025022213h57-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/vlcsnap2025022213h57-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/vlcsnap2025022213h57.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/22/apple-vision-pro-7/vr-mr-ar/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
