        <item>
            <title>【开箱】《人中之龙 8 外传，夏威夷海盗》收藏盒限定版，真岛吾朗毒蛇眼罩超型</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/22/like-a-dragon-2/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=like-a-dragon-2</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/22/like-a-dragon-2/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Gary Lee]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 22 Feb 2025 03:59:48 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[游戏情报]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1293488</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>《人中之龙 8 外传，夏威夷海盗》刚刚发售，小编也取得了中文收藏盒限定版，立即同大家开箱看看。</p><p><a title="_DSC7527" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54342942775/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54342942775_29a3c1e157_b.jpg" alt="_DSC7527" width="1024" height="683" /></a></p><h2>今集外传玩什么？</h2><p>《人中之龙 8 外传，夏威夷海盗》是《人中之龙》系列的外传作品，以系列经典角色真岛吾朗为主角，故事设定在《人中之龙 8》事件结束后的半年，真岛吾朗在一场船难后漂流至一个名为里奇岛的偏远小岛，醒来时发现自己失去了记忆，甚至连名字都无法想起。在少年诺亚·里奇的救助下，真岛开始寻找记忆的线索，并意外卷入一场围绕失落宝藏的冒险。为了找回过去并揭开隐藏的真相，他组建了自己的海盗团，驾驶名为「吾朗丸」的海盗船，航向浩瀚的大海，展开一场惊心动魄的旅程。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293493" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/072-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/072-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/072.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293495" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/022-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/022-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/022.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>游戏的核心玩法延续了《人中之龙》系列的动作冒险传统，并加入了海盗主题的创新元素，让玩家体验陆地与海洋双重战场的乐趣。真岛吾朗拥有两种独特的战斗风格，玩家可根据战况自由切换：</p><p>狂犬风格：延续真岛在系列中的经典形象，以短刀和敏捷的身手进行高速单体攻击，适合应对强敌。这个风格结合拳击、踢击和刀击，可发动空中连击，并使用「疯狂计量表」召唤分身进行组合攻击，效果华丽且强大。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293492" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/032-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/032-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/032.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293496" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/071-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/071-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/071.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>海盗风格：融入海盗元素，使用双持弯刀进行大范围群攻，并能运用三种侧武器：弯刀回旋镖，手枪，链钩。此外，海盗风格还能使用「黑暗乐器」召唤黑暗神祇，例如小提琴召唤食人鲨、萨克斯风召唤鸟类龙卷风、吉他召唤巨猿、陶笛召唤治愈与控制敌人的水母，这些神祇的召唤效果依敌人数量或战场环境而变化。战斗中还有热行动，在特定条件下发动强力攻击，增加战斗的策略性和爽快感。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293491" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/021-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/021-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/021.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293494" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/041-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/041-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/041.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>驾驶吾朗丸海战</h2><p>游戏的一大亮点是玩家可以驾驶「吾朗丸」进行海上探索与战斗。玩家可以操控船只进行炮击，需避开敌方火力，并可使用火箭发射器攻击。船只可通过升级强化甲板、添加火焰喷射器或雷射，增加战斗能力。亦设有登船战，在削弱敌船后，玩家可登船进行近身战斗，利用真岛的能力和船员支援。船员可提供攻击或治疗效果，玩家可招募超过 100 位船员，这些船员可在夏威夷和马德兰蒂斯周围招募。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293497" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/14-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/14-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/14.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293498" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/042-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/042-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/042.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><br /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293499" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/031-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/031-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/031.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>收藏盒限定版开箱</h2><p><a title="_DSC7529" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54342742174/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54342742174_7ef1e450f2_b.jpg" alt="_DSC7529" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><h2>超型毒蛇眼罩</h2><p>限定版几年精品中，小编最为喜爱这件了，印刷精莫的修罗面具盒子内，就是装有皮革制的真岛吾朗毒蛇眼罩，最正的是有条立体的银色毒蛇，又型又靓，当作是 Cosplay 道具应该也非常不错，相信 Fans 看到实物应该也会超喜爱的。</p><p><a title="_DSC7533" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54342758458/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54342758458_dbc1bc1f17_b.jpg" alt="_DSC7533" width="1024" height="683" /></a></p><p><a title="_DSC7536" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54341629947/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54341629947_9344005ddd_b.jpg" alt="_DSC7536" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><h2>插到真岛吾朗弹出来多人玩具</h2><p>这个名为真岛吾朗「危机一发」派对多人玩具，是由玩具厂 Takara Tomy 制作的，可以多人轮流插胶刀仔入木桶，看谁会插到 Q 版真岛吾朗弹出来。</p><p><a title="_DSC7542" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54342942720/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54342942720_ec7bfa88fa_b.jpg" alt="_DSC7542" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><br /><a title="_DSC7543" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54342758398/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54342758398_5a4bd77f02_b.jpg" alt="_DSC7543" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC7548" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54342529571/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54342529571_b75e740432_b.jpg" alt="_DSC7548" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><h2>真岛吾朗海盗亚加力直立牌</h2><p>这是一个 A4 Size 的亚加力胶直立牌，那张画正是游戏盒图那张真岛吾朗海盗画像。</p><h2><a title="_DSC7561" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/202198613@N06/54342529561/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54342529561_ea22bc8485_b.jpg" alt="_DSC7561" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></h2><h2>DLC 序号各种组合包</h2><p>1. 传说海盗船员组合包（能够将桐生一马和堂岛大吾等系列人气角色新增为吾朗海盗团船员）<br />
2. 传说穿搭组合包（能够让主角真岛换上桐生一马和冴岛大河等历代系列人气角色服装，以及本作原创 T-shirt ）<br />
3. 吾朗丸特别自订组合包（能够变更海盗船 「吾朗丸」 外观的零件套组。以桐生一马和春日一番等人气角色为主题设计）<br />
4. 追加卡拉 OK 乐曲 &amp; BGM 组合包（可在卡拉 OK 新增曲目以外，还能获得将人气歌曲当作行走时背景音乐的道具）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293489" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mwtmzvv1_mpwxov8ywwp-694x505.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="505" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mwtmzvv1_mpwxov8ywwp-694x505.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/mwtmzvv1_mpwxov8ywwp.jpg 1236w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/02/22/like-a-dragon-2/game-channel/">【开箱】《人中之龙 8 外传，夏威夷海盗》收藏盒限定版，真岛吾朗毒蛇眼罩超型</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
