        <item>
            <title>V Walk 嘉禾戏院变卖设备，网民入手戏院音响器材、喇叭：「一定系好嘢」</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/21/v-walk/wireless-home/audio-visual/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=v-walk</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/21/v-walk/wireless-home/audio-visual/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 21 Feb 2025 12:00:08 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[影音产品]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[V Walk]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1293443</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>位于南昌的 V Walk 嘉禾戏院近日正式结业，拍卖行开始接手变卖戏院内的设备及物品。市民纷纷前往拍卖场，抢购音响设备、座椅等高质素商品。拍卖行在官方公告后，戏院内的大批音响设备及萤幕已被拆除，部分已被认购。原本用作售票的区域，现已堆满了各种音响设备，甚至包括一些标价不明的物品。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293457" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/480589087_1046636310-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/480589087_1046636310-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/480589087_1046636310.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/480589087_1046636310-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p>去年 12 月底戏院暂停戏票销售，并宣布「暂停营业」，但直至近日才得到确认戏院关闭的消息。随著拍卖活动开始，戏院内的一些设备被标上拍卖价格，包括座椅每张 HK$500、热狗机 HK$3,000，以及汽水柜 HK$2,000。爆谷机和其他设备则未标明价格。</p><p><iframe loading="lazy" style="border: none; overflow: hidden;" src="https://www.facebook.com/plugins/post.php?href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FTaiFookHongHK%2Fposts%2Fpfbid02AC2JpKiEUDruXpKVRPBHHCvPKgi1UruoTGXx6mUfnvNGkHpKqYBVB9LsbqBR9WQPl&amp;show_text=true&amp;width=500" width="500" height="723" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe></p><p>对于这些拍卖物品，市民有著不同的看法。王先生表示，这些从戏院拆下的设备质素一定很高，比市面上许多商品更为可靠。他在拍卖行网站上看到一对心仪的喇叭，发现价格相对优惠，于是便立即前往现场取货。据了解，这些知名品牌设备包括有 JBL 大型喇叭和 Dolby CP750 影院处理器，以及大批荧幕。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293454" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/480701520_1046635687-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/480701520_1046635687-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/480701520_1046635687.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/480701520_1046635687-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293456" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/480652900_1046635757-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/480652900_1046635757-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/480652900_1046635757.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/480652900_1046635757-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293455" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/481063634_1046635690-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/481063634_1046635690-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/481063634_1046635690.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/481063634_1046635690-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293453" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/480642043_1046635590-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/480642043_1046635590-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/480642043_1046635590.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/480642043_1046635590-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p>戏院的其他物品也引起了一些拍卖者的兴趣。除了影院座椅和食品设备，还有一些旧电影纪念品，包括《名侦探柯南》及《阖家辣》等海报、明信片等。办公室内则仍然遗留大量公司财务记录和员工的个人物品，未有完全清理。</p><p>目前，戏院大部分的设备和家具均已进入拍卖流程，并依照法院命令进行处理。拍卖行表示，数天后，该场所将交还给商场，所有未售出的物品将继续处理。</p><p data-start="652" data-end="721">资料来源：<a href="https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/60212836/v-walk%E5%98%89%E7%A6%BE%E6%88%B2%E9%99%A2%E7%B5%90%E6%A5%AD-%E7%9B%B4%E6%93%8A%E8%AE%8A%E8%B3%A3%E7%A0%B4%E5%9C%B0%E7%8D%84%E6%B5%B7%E5%A0%B1-%E7%88%86%E8%B0%B7%E6%A9%9F-%E6%88%B2%E9%99%A2%E6%AB%88%E5%94%AE-500">香港 01</a>, <a href="https://www.facebook.com/TaiFookHongHK/posts/pfbid02AC2JpKiEUDruXpKVRPBHHCvPKgi1UruoTGXx6mUfnvNGkHpKqYBVB9LsbqBR9WQPl">大福行夜冷 Facebook</a></p><p data-start="723" data-end="800"><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/02/21/v-walk/wireless-home/audio-visual/">V Walk 嘉禾戏院变卖设备，网民入手戏院音响器材、喇叭：「一定系好嘢」</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/21/v-walk/wireless-home/audio-visual/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
